    Efficacy and Safety of Dapagliflozin According to Frailty in Heart Failure With Reduced Ejection Fraction : A Post Hoc Analysis of the DAPA-HF Trial.
 Dapagliflozin improved al outcomes examined, regardless of frailty status. However, the absolute reductions were larger in more frail patients. Primary funding source AstraZeneca.
